A little child is going to buy a bar of chocolate from the supermarket .
There are three roads she can choose one to arrive to the supermarket.
In the first way there is a wild dog ..The dog will bite her and then the ambulance will come and take her to the hospital.
In the second way there is a man who will steal her money,then the police will come to investigate.
The third way is safe and she will be able to buy the chocolate and return home.
